Online E-Commerce Website Using Agile
1. Introduction

An Online E-Commerce Website allows customers to purchase products online. It provides a digital platform for sellers and buyers.

2. Objectives

To sell products online

To manage orders and payments

To enhance customer experience

3. Scope

The system includes product listing, cart management, order tracking, and payment integration.

4. Agile Development Process

The project is divided into sprints focusing on product catalog, shopping cart, checkout, and delivery modules.

5. Features

Product search and filter

Shopping cart

Secure payment

Order tracking

6. Benefits

Scalable system

Quick feature updates

Improved customer satisfaction

7. Conclusion

Agile methodology ensures fast development and better quality of the e-commerce platform.
